234
00:20:10,842 --> 00:20:13,111
Half of a person is a companion.

235
00:20:13,779 --> 00:20:15,380
History tells us

236
00:20:15,380 --> 00:20:17,916
when you allow someone into your life,

237
00:20:17,916 --> 00:20:19,985
space is shared,

238
00:20:19,985 --> 00:20:22,187
behaviors are validated,

239
00:20:22,187 --> 00:20:24,690
