the unexpected from the world.

274
00:23:42,422 --> 00:23:45,843
♫ Rescuing the soul ♫

275
00:23:45,843 --> 00:23:49,392
♫ Moving at ten miles per hour ♫

276
00:23:51,008 --> 00:23:54,752
♫ Signals from one universe,
and messages from another ♫

277
00:23:54,752 --> 00:23:59,966
♫ I want to wake up for you ♫

278
00:24:08,547 --> 00:24:10,832
As Martin Luther King once said,

279
00:24:10,832 --> 00:24:13,351
we must accept finite disappointment,

280
00:24:13,919 --> 00:24:16,688
but never lose infinite hope.

281
00:24:18,256 --> 00:24:19,858
What will this relationship

282
00:24:19,858 --> 00:24:21,860
turn out to be?

283
00:24:24,637 --> 00:24:27,808
♫ Without prying eyes ♫

284
00:24:28,374 --> 00:24:31,352
♫ Why the generosity ♫

285
00:24:33,036 --> 00:24:38,117
♫ I know well the color
of yesterday's untold thoughts ♫

286
00:24:38,966 --> 00:24:41,536
♫ Embrace it back ♫

287
00:24:48,576 --> 00:24:52,992
♫ If all the clocks in the world ♫

288
00:24:52,992 --> 00:24:56,317
♫ Were to stop at once ♫

289
00:25:02,432 --> 00:25:07,095
♫ If I could hallucinate a love affair ♫

290
00:25:07,095 --> 00:25:11,597
