♫ That is still surging ♫

291
00:25:23,735 --> 00:25:29,822
♫ If I'm not as kind as you imagined ♫

292
00:25:29,822 --> 00:25:33,664
♫ Would your sorrow ♫

293
00:25:33,664 --> 00:25:37,289
♫ Still linger on my shoulder ♫

294
00:25:38,048 --> 00:25:41,037
♫ The yearning of two people ♫

295
00:25:41,591 --> 00:25:44,749
♫ How much does it weigh ♫

296
00:25:44,749 --> 00:25:47,877
♫ If we stand up at the same time ♫

297
00:25:47,877 --> 00:25:51,269
♫ Can we soar ♫

298
00:25:53,207 --> 00:25:59,146
♫ If I'm not as kind as you imagined ♫

299
00:25:59,146 --> 00:26:03,317
♫ Would you then overturn ♫

300
00:26:03,317 --> 00:26:06,792
♫ Your faith in love ♫

301
00:26:06,792 --> 00:26:10,593
♫ Has anyone not ever been lost ♫

302
00:26:10,593 --> 00:26:14,524
♫ In the vast ocean of humanity ♫

303
00:26:14,524 --> 00:26:17,696
♫ Awaking towards the light of dreams ♫

304
00:26:17,696 --> 00:26:21,059
♫ A grand dream is all it is ♫

305
00:26:22,422 --> 00:26:25,440
♫ Time is adept at revealing ♫

306
00:26:25,440 --> 00:26:28,129
♫ All the truth ♫

307
00:26:29,707 --> 00:26:35,542
♫ The truth forms a high wall ♫

308
00:26:39,531 --> 00:26:41,633
Do you take cold showers? Why?

309
00:26:41,633 --> 00:26:43,368
Every model has locked functions.

310
00:26:43,368 --> 00:26:45,704
If you have special requirements…

311
00:26:45,704 --> 00:26:47,238
You are my first owner.

312
00:26:47,238 --> 00:26:49,474
Taking good care of you is my duty.

313
00:26:49,474 --> 00:26:51,409
It's been almost 30 years

314
00:26:51,409 --> 00:26:53,144
since someone cuddled me.

315
00:27:04,047 --> 00:27:11,191
♫ Turns out that a long time is not forever ♫

316
00:27:11,191 --> 00:27:13,783
♫ A hand held for so long ♫

317
00:27:13,783 --> 00:27:17,825
♫ Has become a hand waving goodbye ♫

318
00:27:17,825 --> 00:27:22,999
♫ The promises so bravely
voiced at the beginning ♫

319
00:27:22,999 --> 00:27:27,087
♫ Have now lost the reason to be fulfilled ♫

320
00:27:27,087 --> 00:27:28,823
♫ A beginning with no end ♫

321
00:27:28,823 --> 00:27:33,143
♫ If we must pursue who's at fault ♫

322
00:27:33,143 --> 00:27:38,862
♫ Blame it all on me ♫

323
00:27:38,862 --> 00:27:42,743
♫ Since words of love are spoken
without a second thought ♫

324
00:27:42,743 --> 00:27:46,803
♫ Why can't I let go with ease ♫

325
